channel.title: SkaScape
channel.description:
[i]Information:[/i] I'm growing bored again on RSPS and RS in general so I'm going to release my current work; SkaScape. I originally started this with around 800KB for the client class, less than 700 now, with all my additions and removal of some junk. I've used alot of switch statements to replace if-statements. Such as I removed a [b]ton[/b] of else-ifs and if-else's in the NpcHandler class; they are now formatted in switch statements. This is a bit unfinished, this is only if you want to work on a server instead of download one and host it right from the get-go. The base is a devolution source.
[i]Features[/i] -Yanille home -Random teleportation (using the misc.random) -Random events -Basic advertiser block; only through regular chat. -Perfect muting (They cannot PM/talk/yell) -Muting players through the report abuse interface -Command class (`Rich stole my idea :p)) -Teleportation class (to save some space in your client class) -Clue scrolls (a few steps) -Following -Sound -Working prayer (NPC's hit less if you've got the correct prayer on) -Working Defence VS NPC (The higher your defence; the lower their hit) -Quite a few lists (Objects, NPC IDs, Item IDs, Co-Ordinates, etc) -Membership (using a file instead of a large boolean of Strings for the player names) -Runecrafting (right click "Teleport" on Aubury in the Varrock rune shop) -Working potions -Herb identifying -Herblore -Thieving (next to no space used, saved spaced with a pickpocketing method)
[i]Images:[/i]
Crandor for PVNPC training [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/Crandor.jpg[/img]
Fight demons by speaking to the Gypsy in Varrock [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/Gypsy1.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/Gypsy2.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/Gypsy3.jpg[/img]
Training for Premium members [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/Prem.jpg[/img]
Visit Shantay's pass in Al-Kharid [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/Shantay1-1.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/Shantay2-1.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/Shantay3.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/Shantay4.jpg[/img]
Why not enjoy some relaxing fishing their aswell; but bring your fishing equipment [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/alkharid1.jpg[/img]
Skillers can pickpocket in peace; no worrying about people killing your thieving NPCs [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/varrock1.jpg[/img]
Change your looks in the SkaScape clothing store [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/varrock2.jpg[/img]
Sell Silverlight to Sir Prysin for some extra cash [IMG]http://i259.photobucket.com/albums/hh310/Mikeyofadown94/varrock3.jpg[/img]
[i]Commands:[/i] Normal players [code] ::loan ##### - Receive a loan for the money you input; cannot be over 500K ::repay - Repay your loan before receiving another ::players - Find out who is online ::yell "" - Send a message to every online player ::password "" - Changes the players' password to the substring [/code]
Player Moderators [code] ::ipban # - Blocks the IP of the Player ID from ::players ::pban # - Permenant ban; only the Owner can revoke this ::tban # - Temporary ban ::tele ### ### - Alters the players' co-ordinates to the integers they input [/code]
Administrators [code] ::vent "" - NPC's will speak ::itemname # - Tells you the name of the integer you input ::npcname # - Tells you the name of the NPC for the integer you input ::master - Their stats are maxed out to 99 ::refill - Fills their Special Bar up ::pickup ### # - Spawns items ::addxp # # - Gives them experience to the Skill/Amount they input [/code]
To see them all; refer to the Command class.
[i]Link:[/i] I have put the .rar archive as an attachment; only registered users may see it.
